Class ApiCall

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.khajas.service.ApiCall
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CricApi, CurrencyApi, DateTimeApi, GetCityLocation, LocationService, Maths, MyIdentification, NewsApi, WeatherInfo, WikiApi

    public abstract class ApiCall
extends Object
    The Following abstract class has code that is common to all services It has one abstract method that all the sub-class must implement It has a static member or array of all intents to be shared among all sub classes
